<inglise> Article 13 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 13 </eesti>
<inglise> Member States or any competent authority they designate as well as the dispute settlement authorities referred to in Article 20 (3) shall have right of access to the accounts of generation, transmission or distribution undertakings which they need to consult in carrying out their checks. </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmesriikidel v&otilde;i nende m&auml;&auml;ratud p&auml;devatel asutustel, sealhulgas artikli 20 l&otilde;ikes 3 nimetatud vaidlusi lahendavatel asutustel on &otilde;igus l&auml;bi vaadata tootmis-, &uuml;lekande- v&otilde;i jaotusettev&otilde;tjate raamatupidamist, kui neil on seda kontrolli tegemiseks vaja. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 14 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 14 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall take the necessary steps to ensure that the accounts of electricity undertakings are kept in accordance with paragraphs 2 to 5. </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmesriigid v&otilde;tavad vajalikud meetmed, et tagada elektriettev&otilde;tjate raamatupidamise vastavus k&auml;esoleva artikli l&otilde;igetele 2-5. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Electricity undertakings, whatever their system of ownership or legal form, shall draw up, submit to audit and publish their annual accounts in accordance with the rules of national law concerning the annual accounts of limited liability companies adopted pursuant to the fourth Council Directive 78/660/EEC of 25 July 1978 based on Article 54 (3) (g) of the Treaty on the annual accounts of certain types of companies (8). Undertakings which are not legally obliged to publish their annual accounts shall keep a copy of these at the disposal of the public in their head office. </inglise>
<eesti> Elektriettev&otilde;tjad peavad olenemata nende omandivormist v&otilde;i &otilde;iguslikust vormist koostama, esitama kontrollimiseks ja avaldama oma raamatupidamise aastaaruanded koosk&otilde;las siseriiklike &otilde;igusnormidega piiratud vastutusega &auml;ri&uuml;hingu raamatupidamise aastaaruannete kohta, mis on vastu v&otilde;etud vastavalt n&otilde;ukogu 25. juuli 1978. aasta neljandale direktiivile 78/660/EM&Uuml;, mis p&otilde;hineb asutamislepingu artikli 54 l&otilde;ike 3 punktil g ja k&auml;sitleb teatavat liiki &auml;ri&uuml;hingute raamatupidamise aastaaruandeid. (8) Ettev&otilde;tjad, kellel ei ole seaduslikku kohustust oma raamatupidamise aastaaruandeid avaldada, peavad hoidma nende koopiad oma peakontoris avalikkusele k&auml;ttesaadavana. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> Integrated electricity undertakings shall, in their internal accounting, keep separate accounts for their generation, transmission and distribution activities, and, where appropriate, consolidated accounts for other, non-electricity activities, as they would be required to do if the activities in question were carried out by separate undertakings, with a view to avoiding discrimination, cross-subsidization and distortion of competition. </inglise>
<eesti> Diskrimineerimise, ristsubsideerimise ja konkurentsi moonutamise v&auml;ltimiseks peavad integreeritud elektriettev&otilde;tjatesiseses raamatupidamises olema eraldi aruanded elektri tootmise, &uuml;lekandmise ja jaotamise kohta ning vajaduse korral konsolideeritud aastaaruanded elektrisektoriv&auml;lise tegevuse kohta nii, nagu neilt n&otilde;utaks juhul, kui k&otilde;nealuse tegevusega oleksid h&otilde;ivatud eri ettev&otilde;tjad. </eesti>
<inglise> They shall include a balance sheet and a profit and loss account for each activity in notes to their accounts. </inglise>
<eesti> Sisemine raamatupidamine peab raamatupidamisaruannete lisades sisaldama iga tegevuse bilanssi ja kasumiaruannet. </eesti>
<inglise> 4. </inglise>
<eesti> 4. </eesti>
<inglise> Undertakings shall specify in notes to the annual accounts the rules for the allocation of assets and liabilities and expenditure and income which they follow in drawing up the separate accounts referred to in paragraph 3. </inglise>
<eesti> Raamatupidamise aastaaruannete lisades t&auml;psustavad ettev&otilde;tjad eeskirjad, mis k&auml;sitlevad varade ja kohustuste ning kulude ja tulude jaotamist ja mida nad j&auml;rgivad l&otilde;ikes 3 nimetatud eraldi aruannete koostamisel. </eesti>
<inglise> These rules may be amended only in exceptional cases. </inglise>
