<inglise> Such amendments must be mentioned in the notes and must be duly substantiated. </inglise>
<eesti> Muudatused peavad olema aastaaruannete lisades nimetatud ja n&otilde;uetekohaselt p&otilde;hjendatud. </eesti>
<inglise> 5. </inglise>
<eesti> 5. </eesti>
<inglise> The annual accounts shall indicate in notes any transaction of a certain size conducted with affiliated undertakings, within the meaning of Article 41 of the seventh Council Directive 83/349/EEC of 13 June 1983 based on Article 54 (3) (g) of the Treaty on consolidated accounts (9), or with associated undertakings, within the meaning of Article 33 (1) thereof, or, with undertakings which belong to the same shareholders. </inglise>
<eesti> Raamatupidamise aastaaruannete lisades esitatakse k&otilde;ik sidusettev&otilde;tjatega sooritatud olulised tehingud asutamislepingu artikli 54 l&otilde;ike 3 punktil g p&otilde;hineva konsolideeritud aastaaruandeid k&auml;sitleva n&otilde;ukogu 13. juuni 1983. aasta seitsmenda direktiivi 83/349/EM&Uuml; artikli 41 t&auml;henduses (9) v&otilde;i &uuml;hisettev&otilde;tjatega sooritatud olulised tehingud selle direktiivi artikli 33 l&otilde;ike 1 t&auml;henduses v&otilde;i samadele osanikele/aktsion&auml;ridele kuuluvate ettev&otilde;tjatega sooritatud olulised tehingud; </eesti>
<inglise> Article 15 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 15 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Member States which designate as a single buyer a vertically integrated electricity undertaking or part of a vertically integrated electricity undertaking shall lay down provisions requiring the single buyer to operate separately from the generation and distribution activities of the integrated undertaking. </inglise>
